  Stable for x86, wrt bug #544156

  27 Mar 2015; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> libmirage-3.0.3.ebuild:
  Stable for amd64, wrt bug #544156

*libmirage-3.0.3 (21 Feb 2015)

  21 Feb 2015; Alexandre Rostovtsev <tetromino@gentoo.org>
  -libmirage-2.1.0.ebuild, +libmirage-3.0.3.ebuild,
  -files/libmirage-2.1.0-DISABLE_DEPRECATED.patch:
  Version bump, adds image writing (bug #518590, thanks to Rafał Mużyło).
  Punt old.

  26 Jan 2014; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> libmirage-2.1.1.ebuild:
  Stable for x86, wrt bug #494802

  19 Jan 2014; Pacho Ramos <pacho@gentoo.org> libmirage-2.1.1.ebuild:
  amd64 stable, bug 494802

  08 Oct 2013; Alexandre Rostovtsev <tetromino@gentoo.org>
  -files/libmirage-2.0.0-gtk-doc.patch:
  Remove old patch.

